ygData.messageBody:
Solo: Chain-Fear: South Karana Avo's and Chargers (maybe coursairs); the odd
Tesch Mal Gnoll; Goblin Headmaster in Lake Rathe. Charm: Choon & Froon
(maybe green - not sure); HG/Grif in NK; HG/Grif in EK; HG Rathe Mts.

Groups: Sol-B, Lower Guk Live and Dead side, SplitPaw, Kithkor, Spectres in
Oasis, Bouncers in Ogg. Freeport guards, Qeynos guards. Maybe some gobs in
Perma King room. Ice giants. Kedge.

Not alot of options and it only gets worse.

Sylly.
